Software Specification

Sensor data {B}
- sound [0~255]
- light [0~255]
- temperature [0~255]
- people [0~500]
- window [0,1]

Feedback type 
- positive: give candies {A}
- negative: sound negative feedback {C}
- sound: accumulated sound {D}
- sound_level: different tone sound feedback (customized) {0-9}

---------------------------------------------------
5 Machine w/ sensors

NO.1: 
input: 5 sensor (people, microphone, temperature, light, window) + switch + pin package
output: speaker
(no noise)

NO.2 ~ NO.5:
the same input/output
(noise)

(NO.5 - broken motor, driver board)




